| Make it obvious, if we have loaded a target compiler, when we are in host
| mode instead.

forth

( set prompt in interpret mode)
-: ."  (host)" ;   state @  cell+ !

( set prompt in compile mode)
-: ."  (host compiling)" ;   ' ] >body cell+ !
